{
  "stem": "6052.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we are sure what happened with France and with Holland and with Denmark.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, the beginning-- Poland and in Italy and Greece and other countries.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Any other questions with regard to this point?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, this is that they had to-- what they did over there with this group which arrived in Riga was that they were forced to walk long distances in this cold, dreadful weather.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my sisters were very little girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know how and what-- how they arrived and if they arrived in the Lager, which was also a dreadful place to live.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But these details I am not aware.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the details I am aware of are the most horrible picture I could conceive in my lifetime.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And thinking back how dreadful it was for my father to die in Dachau, after all the descriptions and after all I read, this may have been equally dreadful over there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you really cannot take measure what was worse because all was a terrible thing which happened under the Nazi regime.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have pictures of my sisters and documents which show--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was related in a book, not a neighbor we knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A-- somebody who lived there and who I did not know and do not know and still don't know related a story about what happened to the [?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Todestransport ?] to Riga, to Riga [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody related it in a story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is where from I learned these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When this book was published, I-- a friend of Leipzig who lives in New York told me about this book.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ordered it from the Israelitische Religionsgemeinde.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They send it to me, and here I read all the stories, which is-- which are authentic, of course.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
